<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَيَقُولُ سُبْحَانَ الَّذِي ذَا صُنْعُه<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سُبْحَانَ مُتْقِنِ صَنْعَةَ الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكِلاهُمَا مَرَآةُ صَاحِبِهِ إِذَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا شَاءَ يُبْصِر وَجْهَهُ يَرَيَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَرَى مَحَاسِنَ وَجْهِهِ فِي وَجْهِهَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَتَرَى مَحَاسِنَهَا بِهِ بِعَيْنَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حُمْرُ الْخُدُودِ ثُغُورُهُنَّ لآلِئ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سُودُ الْعُيُونِ فَوَاتِرُ الأَجْفَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَالْبَدْرُ يَبْدُو حِينَ يَبْسُمُ ثَغْرُهَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَيُضِيءُ سَقْفُ الْقَصْرِ بِالْجِدْرَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلَقَدْ رَوَيْنَا أَنَّ بَرْقًا سَاطِعًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يَبْدُو فَيَسْأَلُ عَنْهُ مَنْ بِجِنَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَيُقَالُ هَذَا ضَوْءُ ثَغْرٍ ضَاحِكٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فِي الْجَنَّةِ الْعُلْيَا كَمَا تَرَيَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>للهِ لاثِمُ ذَلِكَ الثَّغْرِ الَّذِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فِي لَثْمِهِ إِدْرَاكُ كُلِّ أَمَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>رَيَّانَةُ الأَعْطَافِ مِنْ مَاءِ الشَّبَا ... ???? ... بِ فَغُصْنُهَا بِالْمَاءِ ذُو جَرَيَانِ ... ???? ... لما جَرَى مَاءُ الشَّبَابِ بِغُصْنِهَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>حَمَلَ الثِّمَارَ كَثِيرَةَ الأَلْوَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَالْوَرْدُ وَالتُّفَّاحُ وَالرُّمَّانُ فِي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
